---
title: BBQ Pork and Pepper Stew with chipotle sauce and cheese
description: This stew is simple to prepare yet features layers of complimentary flavour profiles that come together to take your tastebuds on a journey. This is a substantial dish with bell pepper and pork mince at its heart that is both filling and flavourful.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R18_W12_IE_IEXQP21701-3_MAIN_high-41261742.jpg
